  <refentry id="function.shuffle">
   <refnamediv>
    <refname>shuffle</refname>
    <refpurpose>배열을 뒤섞는다</refpurpose>
   </refnamediv>
   <refsect1>
    <title>설명</title>
     <methodsynopsis>
      <type>void</type><methodname>shuffle</methodname>
      <methodparam><type>array</type><parameter>array</parameter></methodparam>
     </methodsynopsis>
    <para>
     이 함수는 배열을 (배열 안의 원소를 임의의 순서로) 뒤섞는다.
     <function>srand</function>를 사용하여 이 함수를 초기화해야 한다.
     <example>
      <title><function>shuffle</function> 예제코드</title>
      <programlisting role="php">
<![CDATA[
<?php
$numbers = range (1,20);
srand ((float)microtime()*1000000);
shuffle ($numbers);
while (list (, $number) = each ($numbers)) {
    echo "$number ";
}
?>
]]>
      </programlisting>
     </example>
    </para>
    
    &note.randomseed;
    
    <para>
     <function>arsort</function>, <function>asort</function>,
     <function>ksort</function>, <function>rsort</function>,
     <function>sort</function>, <function>usort</function> 참고.
    </para>
   </refsect1>
  </refentry>

